.TH "SVGAELEMENT.PROTOCOL" "3JS" "October 21, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
SVGAElement.protocol \- SVGAElement: protocol property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]protocol\f[B]\f[R] property of the \f[CR]SVGAElement\f[R]
interface returns a string representing the protocol component,
including trailing colon (\f[CR]:\f[R]), of the referenced URL.
.PP
This property can be set, to change the URL\(cqs protocol.
.SH VALUE
A string.
